<lb ed="L" n="0042b11"/><cb:div type="w"><head>音釋</head>
<lb ed="L" n="0042b12"/><cb:div type="note"><entry><form><term rend="no_nor"><g ref="#CB15409">𠿕</g></term></form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL158p0042b1202" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">苦弔切音竅不安妥也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>吻</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL158p0042b1212" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">武粉切音刎口脣邊曰吻</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>濼</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL158p0042b1223" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">弼各切音
<lb ed="L" n="0042b13"/>薄陂澤也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>桎梏</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL158p0042b1307" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">上職日切音質足械也下古祿切音谷手械也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>蜒蚰</form>
<lb ed="L" n="0042b14"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pL158p0042b1401" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">上夷然切音延下于求切音尤蜒蚰蟲名</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>戩</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL158p0042b1418" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">子淺切音剪福祥也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry></cb:div></cb:div>
